title: Yaradullu
content:
41°01′N 45°26′E﻿ / ﻿41.017°N 45.433°E﻿ / 41.017; 45.433

Yaradullu is a village in the Agstafa Rayon of Azerbaijan. The village forms part of the municipality of Tatlı.[1]
